verses.text:
For Zedekiah king of Judah had shut him up, saying, “Why do you
prophesy, and say, ‘The LORD says, “Behold, I will give this city into the hand of the king of Babylon,
and he will take it;

and Zedekiah king of Judah won’t escape out of the hand of the Chaldeans,
but will surely be delivered into the hand of the king of Babylon, and will speak with him mouth to mouth,
and his eyes will see his eyes;

great in counsel, and mighty in work; whose eyes are open to all the
ways of the children of men, to give everyone according to his ways, and according to the fruit of his
doings;
